= Dragon Warrior IV (NES) Text Table =

This page documents the text encoding for '''Dragon Warrior IV''' (NES, US version).

== Overview ==

Dragon Warrior IV uses a custom text encoding. Each character in the game's text corresponds to a tile in the font graphics.

