== Usage Examples ==

=== Simple Message ===

<pre>
Hello[LINE]World![END]
</pre>

Hex: <code>07 1E 25 25 28 01 16 28 2B 25 1D 42 00</code>

=== Dynamic Text ===

<pre>
[HERO] found[LINE][ITEM]![END]
</pre>

Hex: <code>03 FF 1F 28 2E 27 1D 01 04 42 00</code>

=== Page Break ===

<pre>
This is page one.[PAGE]This is page two.[END]
</pre>

== Thinktank File Format ==

For use with common ROM hacking tools, create a .tbl file:

<pre>
00=A
01=B
02=C
...
1A=a
1B=b
...
34=0
35=1
...
3E=.
3F=,
FF= 
</pre>

